SAMD21
- SERCOM SPI
  - Registers to select pinout
  - Clock must be 1 or 3
  - MOSI must be 0, 2, 3
  - DOPO 0 == PAD[0] = MOSI, PAD[1] = SCK
  - seems easy
  - set DIPO to 3 for PAD[3] as MISO (NC)
  - Port config for _SS
  - SERCOM1 on 17-20? [0:3]
  Take 2:
  - Any pin can be DI
  - CK can be 1/3
  - DO Can be 0, 2, 3

  Ideal:
  DO, CK, CS?
  DOPO 0

- SERCOM USART
  - TXPO 0, TxD on PAD[0]
  - RXPO 1, RxD on Pad[1]
  - PA08-11/Pins 11-14

